{"trainType":"交叉培养","grade":"2020","education":{"id":2,"nameZh":"本科"},"studentType":{"id":4,"nameZh":"普通"},"department":{"id":422,"code":"025","nameZh":"科技传播系"},"major":{"id":863,"code":"02501","nameZh":"传播学"},"majorDirection":null,"requiredCredits":0,"awardDegree":false,"beginSemester":"2020年秋季学期","directionGen":true,"moduleTree":[{"self":{"id":31752,"parent":31751,"type":"必修","typeEn":"Compulsory Courses","major":"--","majorDirection":"--","remark":null,"requiredSubModuleNum":0,"requiredCredits":15,"requiredCourseNum":5,"creditsUpperLimit":null,"courseNumUpperLimit":null,"courses":[{"compulsory":true,"weeks":18,"totalPeriods":60,"theoryPeriods":60,"praticePeriods":0,"experimentPeriods":0,"periodsPerWeek":3,"course":{"id":15032,"code":"025174","nameZh":"科技写作","nameEn":"Scientific and Technical Writing","totalPeriods":60,"theoryPeriods":60,"credits":3,"introduction":"本课程共分三篇十章。第1章“绪论”介绍了科技写作的基本概念、特征、种类和作用，以及科技写作课的任务和方法；第一篇“过程论”三章，介绍了科技写作的准备阶段、行文阶段和修改阶段的的基本知识。第二篇“文体论”四章，讲述科技学术类文体、科技应用类文体、科技新闻类文体和科技普及类文体写作的基本知识。第三篇“作者论”两章，讲述科技写作作者的素质、修养、能力的内涵、内容构成和自我提高的方法。","courseGradation":"专业核心","seasons":"秋,春"},"terms":["3秋"],"remark":null,"examMode":"大作业（论文、报告、项目或作品等）","department":{"id":422,"code":"025","nameZh":"科技传播系"}},{"compulsory":true,"weeks":18,"totalPeriods":60,"theoryPeriods":60,"praticePeriods":0,"experimentPeriods":0,"periodsPerWeek":4,"course":{"id":7131,"code":"025166","nameZh":"传媒管理","nameEn":"Media Management","totalPeriods":60,"theoryPeriods":60,"credits":3,"introduction":"本课程主要讲授传媒管理的基本概念和原理，包括传媒业基本特征和规律、传媒政策法规、传媒战略管理、传媒行业概况等模块。本课程强调传媒管理的实践规律和分析模型在传媒业的运用，通过课堂分组作业、案例分析、课堂演讲等形式增强学生对传媒业的认识，为学生在传媒业立足打下基础，并提供未来职业生涯指导。","courseGradation":"专业核心","seasons":"秋,春"},"terms":["3秋"],"remark":null,"examMode":"大作业（论文、报告、项目或作品等）","department":{"id":422,"code":"025","nameZh":"科技传播系"}},{"compulsory":true,"weeks":18,"totalPeriods":80,"theoryPeriods":40,"praticePeriods":0,"experimentPeriods":40,"periodsPerWeek":3,"course":{"id":14960,"code":"025175","nameZh":"三维动画与特效","nameEn":"3D 